 2. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the right of the owner of the horse##1
 3. the person eating zucchini is the person driving the scooter##1
 4. the person driving the boat is on the right of the old-henry-smoker##1
 5. the tiparillo-smoker is on the left or right of the person drinking milk##3
 6. the person drinking hot-chocolate is the owner of the lizard##1
 7. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is card-games##3
 8. the old-henry-smoker is in an even position##4
 9. the prince-smoker is on the right of the old-henry-smoker##1
10. the old-henry-smoker is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2      |     3      |
